name: Restaurang Tranan
desc: A place to meet at, have a bite to eat and something to drink. That was how Tranan was know in 1929 by the residents of Stockholm, and that’s how it’s still known today - over 80 years later.

name: Miss Clara
desc: The kitchen’s philosophy is to work in as natural way as possible. They change our meat, fish and vegetarian dishes every week.

name: Raw Sushi & Grill
desc: Japan meets Europe in an elegant restaurant focusing on the rawness. At Raw sushi and sashimi coexists with hot dishes from the grill, bothmeat and shellfish.

name: Hamburgarstugan
desc: Come to Hamburgerstugan and get your life's best burger experience. They compile every burger with love daily. You get a day-to-day high-rise burger with home-made dressings and dip sauces. Gluten free bread is available.

name: Masala Masala
desc: Masala Masala – Genuine Indian cuisine, also inspired by its neighboring countries. Our innovative chef has specially composed a number of new vegan dishes.

name: Babel Deli
desc: Babel is today both on Kungstensgatan at Sveavägen and on Långholmsgatan at Hornstull. Welcome to a fantastic dining experience guaranteed by Mamma Etimad!

name: Arirang
desc: Mild or spicy. Gentle and sweet or tantalisingly hot. Anything is possible at Arirang. You can choose how to combine our dishes yourself or you can ask us for advice.
